**Comment:**
[Which principle violated, why it weakens writing]

**Original:**
```
[Full sentence(s) — typically 2-4 sentences for rhythm analysis]
```

**Proposed Revision:**
```
[Complete revised passage]
```

**Why better:**
- [Specific improvement 1]
- [Specific improvement 2]
```

